---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Ticker from '../components/Ticker.astro';
import Portrait from '../components/Portrait.astro';
import Glyph from '../components/Glyph.astro';
import Illustration from '../components/Illustration.astro';
import NextSteps from '../components/NextSteps.astro';

const tickerItems = ['Psychodynamic', 'Attachment-Based', 'Depth-Oriented', 'Relational', 'Collaborative'];

const whoIWorkWith = ['Teens', 'Young Adults', 'Adults', 'Creatives', 'Professionals', 'Grad Students', 'Couples', 'Groups'];
const whatITreat = ['Depression', 'Anxiety', 'Religious Issues', 'Identity', 'Self-Expression', 'Attachment', 'Trauma', 'Shame', 'Grief & Loss', 'Life Transitions', 'Relationship Issues'];
---

<Layout
  title="My Approach — Depth-Oriented Psychotherapy | Nikole Sparks"
  description="Psychodynamic, attachment-based, depth-oriented therapy. Explore your past, own your present, build your future."
  active="/approach/"
  path="/approach/"
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="col">
      <p class="eyebrow">Effective, depth-oriented psychotherapy</p>
      <h1>Explore your past. <br>Own your present. <br><em>Build your future.</em></h1>
      <p>
        We all carry stories that shape how we think, feel, and connect. Deep change happens
        when we honor the full range of our lived experiences and make sense of the narratives
        shaping our lives.
      </p>
      <a class="cta" href="/contact/">Schedule a free consultation →</a>
    </div>
    <Illustration name="depth" size="clamp(240px, 34vw, 380px)" class="hero-illustration" />
  </section>

  <Ticker items={tickerItems} label="Modalities" />

  <!-- Philosophy -->
  <section class="section split c-narrow-wide">
    <div class="col gap-20">
      <p class="eyebrow">MY APPROACH</p>
      <h2 class="h2-serif">Connecting deeper,<br><em>living freer.</em></h2>
      <Glyph name="target-ellipses" class="mt-16" />
    </div>
    <div class="prose prose-15" style="gap:24px;">
      <p>We are shaped by the relationships, experiences, and stories that surround us. Some of these stories bring connection and belonging while others leave imprints of pain, shame, or self-doubt. [...]
      <p>Psychodynamic therapy offers a pathway to work through persistent challenges with anxiety, depression, intimacy and closeness, unprocessed loss, patterns of self-sabotage, emotional expressio[...]
      <p>Many of the people I work with come to therapy looking for answers to the deep questions about why they're struggling, or when their best attempts to change on their own aren't working. W[...]
      <p>The goal is to help you notice the patterns that may be holding you back, understand how they affect your relationships and choices, and free you to inhabit your life in a way that feels true[...]
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Quote -->
  <section class="quote-block">
    <Glyph name="rings" class="hero-figure" />
    <div class="col gap-28">
      <blockquote>"Not until we are lost do we begin to <em>understand</em> ourselves."</blockquote>
      <cite>Henry David Thoreau</cite>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Areas of focus -->
  <section class="section sage on-color">
    <div class="section-heading">
      <div class="stack">
        <p class="eyebrow on-color">Services</p>
        <h2 class="serif" style="font-size:48px; line-height:1.1">Areas of focus</h2>
      </div>
      <p>I work with adults and teens who are seeking a deeper understanding of themselves and their emotional lives.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="split c-1-1" style="align-items:start; gap:72px; margin-bottom:56px">
      <div class="pill-block">
        <div class="label">Who I work with</div>
        <div class="pill-row">{whoIWorkWith.map((p) => <span class="pill">{p}</span>)}</div>
      </div>
      <div class="pill-block">
        <div class="label">What I treat</div>
        <div class="pill-row">{whatITreat.map((p) => <span class="pill">{p}</span>)}</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card-row">
      <a class="service-card primary" href="/services/individual-therapy/"><span>Individual therapy</span><span aria-hidden="true">→</span></a>
      <a class="service-card secondary" href="/services/couples-therapy/"><span>Couples therapy</span><span aria-hidden="true">→</span></a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What to expect -->
  <section class="section split c-media">
    <Portrait placeholder="Office or session photo" accent="bl" />
    <div class="col">
      <p class="eyebrow">What to expect</p>
      <h2 class="h2-serif">Our work <em>together.</em></h2>
      <p class="body">Healing unfolds in its own time. Our work together will honor this natural rhythm, building trust and welcoming all parts of your experience. I approach each person with highly p[...]
      <p class="body">We'll meet regularly to create a space where both the spoken and unspoken aspects of your experience can be understood with curiosity and care. Our work is collaborative, worki[...]
      <a class="text-link" href="/about/">About Nikole →</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <NextSteps
    heading="Getting <em>started.</em>"
    copy="If what you've read sounds interesting to you, I invite you to reach out. I offer a free 15-minute consultation to give you a chance to ask questions and get a feel for how we might work t[...]
  />
</Layout>
